00:41:02.080 --> 00:41:05.800 line:90% position:50% align:middle
<c.white>Dus ik had echt het idee</c>
<c.white>dat je mij wilde laten lachen.</c>

00:41:06.000 --> 00:41:08.360 line:90% position:50% align:middle
