00:41:28.200 --> 00:41:29.800 line:90% position:50% align:middle
<c.cyan>Je deed het echt expres.</c>

00:41:30.000 --> 00:41:31.480 line:90% position:50% align:middle
<c.white>Ja. </c><c.cyan>Oke.</c>

00:41:31.680 --> 00:41:33.680 line:90% position:50% align:middle
<c.white>Maar ik zag wel wat het met je deed.</c>

00:41:33.880 --> 00:41:36.160 line:90% position:50% align:middle
